items.badge_description: It's New Brew Thursday! Drink a new beer on three Thursdays in a 30 day period! Find out how New Brew Thursday was started, and catch up on old episodes.

Some may argue that wine is better than beer, especially in a country so well known for its vineyards. We all know theyre wrong. Cheers! Thats 200 different beers from a brewery in Italy. Try 5 more for Level 41.

user.bio: ...A dream is purer than an obsession. There is pride in a dream, anywhere in the world....

Life is too short to drink industrial beer!
Fav styles: IPA/APA/DIPA/BIPA/ISA, Stout/Porter/IS/IP. New beers everyday.
